This time, the main focus was on the work scene, so there was
no problem with the characters appearing in the picture, 

06:12.000 --> 06:15.500
and it was okay to release a video introducing the lab.

06:16.500 --> 06:19.000
Yes, no problem.

06:19.000 --> 06:25.000
It’s good.
